room_title: Escape room " Down the Rabbit Hole" by Escape Room Zone in Detroit
room_address: 31401 John R Rd Madison Heights, MI 48071
room_description: You’ve gone down the rabbit hole and things keep getting curiouser and curiouser! You’re trying to find the white rabbit but you don’t know which way to go! The Cheshire Cat says ask the Mad Hatter, the Mad Hatter says ask the Queen, and the Queen says, “Off with your head!” To get out, read the directions and directly you will be directed in the right direction. Most everyone’s mad here, are you all there yourself?
